<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased API Error Rates>
We're investigating increased error rates for DynamoDB APIs in the US-EAST-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Latencies>
We are investigating increased Workmail Outlook latencies in the US-EAST-1 Region impacting the sending and receiving of new messages or appointments in Outlook clients.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased API Error Rates>
Between 10:10 AM and 11:23 AM PDT we experienced increased error rates for DynamoDB APIs in the US-EAST-1 Region. The issue is resolved and the service is operating normally.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Latencies>
Between 10:16 AM and 11:07 AM PST we experienced degraded WorkMail Outlook performances in the US-EAST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
